sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant G as GraphQL
    participant A as Auth Service
    participant S as Supabase
    participant D as Database
    
    C->>G: login(email, password)
    G->>A: authenticate
    A->>S: signInWithPassword
    S-->>A: session + user
    A->>D: findUserByAuthId
    D-->>A: user data
    A-->>G: combined result
    G-->>C: token + user